____________________  How to push DOcker images to DockerHUb _____________________________

My DockerHub account details  
shilpajoshi6789@gmail.com
Docker@1997

Steps are as follows ----->
docker login 
Uname : DockerHub account ka username  ex shilpajoshidocker
Pswd  : DockerHub account login karne ke liye jo pswd liya tha  ex Docker@1997
docker tag <existing-image> <hub-user>/<repo-name>[:<tag>]
docker push <hub-user>/<repo-name>:<tag>

__________________ How to push Docker images to ACR ________________________
https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/container-registry/container-registry-get-started-docker-cli?tabs=azure-cli

Images mne ek folder mei le lee sari DockerHub sei 
docker images --> Apni images ke names dekh le 
d tag imagename(docker images sei mere ek img le re) myregistry.azurecr.io(Login server hei yeh ACR ka Overview mei dekh)/folder1(in Which I Want My Img)/myimgname(I want 2 Give Now)
d push myregistry.azurecr.io(Login server hei yeh ACR ka)/folder1/myimageIGiveNow

